{"tid":466774,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［理性討論］永恆乾冰可否製造","createTime":"2017-11-13T01:24:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T09:07:38.000Z","uid":43370,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"bdb537730f18a3a0da31d18712996137af6b715a","tid":466774,"uid":43370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:24:12.000Z","msg":"係咁既 以前返工要用到乾冰<br />\n發現黎貨佢係一箱箱用發泡膠盒放<br />\n放成個星期都得<br />\n<br />\n有日就諗<br />\n發泡睇氣溫令乾冰冇變返氣體<br />\n<br />\n如果<br />\n我地用一個方形鐵盒，填滿乾冰<br />\n再完美地封口<br />\n1. 要確保鐵盒夠厚夠力<br />\n2. 要確保完全密封<br />\n<br />\n金屬可以傳熱 都可以傳凍<br />\n入面既乾冰冇空間氣化，會一直保持乾冰形態<br />\n<br />\n結論：呢個鐵盒會永遠保持低溫？"},{"pid":"12960d1eded3a4a49cc3db40ef9f626b4ea96f04","tid":466774,"uid":110892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:42:04.000Z","msg":"見證一個偉大既POST誕生"},{"pid":"3b523cc77bbf24fe9b5bcd3a91de3c6fe1e31ff8","tid":466774,"uid":33213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T02:28:27.000Z","msg":"你啲CO2會溶<br />\n我係咪認真咗"},{"pid":"eb13dd79fd060ffea6f7c8d3a4c65ba091e9a927","tid":466774,"uid":135692,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T03:00:41.000Z","msg":"傳凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"544a693fc84c5cbd5713161449b42b4e1fd2b5ca","tid":466774,"uid":41887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T03:24:46.000Z","msg":"夠厚夠硬=高壓？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae7f8b66de8986329677cca7c89f36525dd484cf","tid":466774,"uid":76018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T03:26:03.000Z","msg":"。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"213e5c81aeb4671bb0a68109cfbb1764029c2a8b","tid":466774,"uid":27143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T03:27:43.000Z","msg":"會溶"},{"pid":"dee7cff6a0ea8ece400f4d382ac8757f29d197c5","tid":466774,"uid":79427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"